===Format===
* '''BGIS 2025 - The Grind:''''' February 5th - 23rd, 2025
** 64 Invited Teams, 16 matchdays.
** Teams divided into 4 groups with 16 squads in each group.
** Each group will play 24 matches in respective weeks.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|'''All 64 teams'''}} based on the overall standings will seed to '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2025|BGIS 2025: Main Event]]'''

