===Allocations===
* {{Bgcolortext|up|'''Top 8 teams'''}} from ''Group A'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[https://liquipedia.net/pubgmobile/Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2025 BGIS 2025: Quarter Finals]'''
* {{Bgcolortext|up|'''Top 8'''}} from ''Group B'' & {{Bgcolortext|stayup|'''Bottom 8'''}} from ''Group A'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[https://liquipedia.net/pubgmobile/Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2025 BGIS 2025: Round 4]'''
* {{Bgcolortext|up|'''Top 8'''}} from ''Group C'' & {{Bgcolortext|stayup|'''Bottom 8'''}} from ''Group B'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[https://liquipedia.net/pubgmobile/Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2025 BGIS 2025: Round 3]'''
* {{Bgcolortext|up|'''Top 8'''}} from ''Group D'' & {{Bgcolortext|stayup|'''Bottom 8'''}} from ''Group C'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[https://liquipedia.net/pubgmobile/Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2025 BGIS 2025: Round 2]'''
* {{Bgcolortext|stay|'''Bottom 8 teams'''}} from ''Group D'' qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india series}} '''[https://liquipedia.net/pubgmobile/Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2025 BGIS 2025: Round 1]'''

